Subject: [PATCH] f2fs: fix to do sanity check on node footer for non inode
 dnode
References: bsc#1012628 CVE-2025-40025 bsc#1252766
Patch-mainline: 6.17.2
Git-commit: c18ecd99e0c707ef8f83cace861cbc3162f4fdf1

